.DT
perform
Discworld player help
perform

.SH Name
.SI 5
perform - Performing a ritual
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
perform <ritual> [from <holy item>] [at|on <target|targets>]
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Perform is used when you want to perform a ritual that you have been taught or
found imbued in an item on your adventures.

Note that the name of the spell/ritual is case sensitive, and should be
typed exactly as you see it with the rituals commands.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> perform light on frog
The frog glows.
> perform heal on khaos
Khaos looks much healthier.
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
rituals
.EI
